      &lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; aria-label=&quot;Next&quot;&gt;
        &lt;span aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&amp;raquo;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
      &lt;&#x2F;a&gt;
    &lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
  &lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;nav&gt;
</code></pre></figure>

  <h3>Disabled and active states</h3>
  <p>Links are customizable for different circumstances. Use <code>.disabled</code> for unclickable links and <code>.active</code> to indicate the current page.</p>
  <div class="bs-example" data-example-id="disabled-active-pagination">
    <nav>
      <ul class="pagination">
        <li class="disabled"><a href="#" aria-label="Previous"><span aria-hidden="true">&laquo;</span></a></li>
        <li class="active"><a href="#">1 <span class="sr-only">(current)</span></a></li>
        <li><a href="#">2</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">3</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">4</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">5</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" aria-label="Next"><span aria-hidden="true">&raquo;</span></a></li>
     </ul>
   </nav>
  </div>
<div class="zero-clipboard"><span class="btn-clipboard">Copy</span></div><figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="html">
&lt;nav&gt;
  &lt;ul class=&quot;pagination&quot;&gt;
    &lt;li class=&quot;disabled&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; aria-label=&quot;Previous&quot;&gt;&lt;span aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&amp;laquo;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
    &lt;li class=&quot;active&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;1 &lt;span class=&quot;sr-only&quot;&gt;(current)&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
    ...
  &lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;nav&gt;
</code></pre></figure>
  <p>You can optionally swap out active or disabled anchors for <code>&lt;span&gt;</code>, or omit the anchor in the case of the previous/next arrows, to remove click functionality while retaining intended styles.</p>
<div class="zero-clipboard"><span class="btn-clipboard">Copy</span></div><figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="html">
&lt;nav&gt;
  &lt;ul class=&quot;pagination&quot;&gt;
    &lt;li class=&quot;disabled&quot;&gt;
      &lt;span&gt;
        &lt;span aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&amp;laquo;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
      &lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
    &lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
    &lt;li class=&quot;active&quot;&gt;
      &lt;span&gt;1 &lt;span class=&quot;sr-only&quot;&gt;(current)&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
    &lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
    ...
  &lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;nav&gt;
</code></pre></figure>


  <h3>Sizing</h3>
